Package com.jotrorox.jtoml.types

Class TomlFloat

java.lang.Object
com.jotrorox.jtoml.types.TomlType
com.jotrorox.jtoml.types.TomlFloat
public class TomlFloat extends TomlType
Represents a TOML Float

This class represents a TOML float. It is used to store TOML floats and convert them to TOML strings.

Since:
0.2
